dct_title_s: EUROPE Divided into its Principall States which are Subdivided into their Principall Provinces
dct_description_sm: European continent, including Great Britain and northern part of Africa.

Part of a set of four continental maps. The other 3 titles are: A New and Exact Map of AFRICA according to the Best Observations, A NEW MAP OF AMERICA according to the Best and Latest Observations, and A New and Exact Map of ASIA according to the Best Observations.
Additional title along map top: : A NEW MAP OF EUROPE DIVIDED INTO ITS PRINCIPALL KINGDOMS AND COUNTRIES. Described By Sanson Geogr to Ye French King.

Dedication within title cartouche: To the Serene and Most Sacred Majesty ANNE By the Grace of God Queen of Great Brittain, France, & Ireland, This Map is Humbly Dedicat.d & Presented by Yr Maj.ties Loyal Subject and Servant Henry Overton.
Title cartouche of coat of arms flanked by man and woman carrying shields, scrollwork, and small picture of a horse.
